---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mentorship - Kalthoff Performance">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">Mentorship</h1>
      
      <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] mb-12 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Mentorship and professional development" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
          I am passionate about developing the next generation of strength and conditioning coaches, sport scientists, and performance professionals. Through mentorship opportunities, I provide guidance on training methodologies, data analysis, and career development in the high-performance and general fitness industries. Whether working with young professionals looking to break into the field or experienced practitioners aiming to refine their approach, my goal is to share practical knowledge and real-world insights that foster growth and success.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What's Included</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>One-on-one mentorship sessions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Career development guidance</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Training methodology review</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Data analysis and interpretation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Professional networking opportunities</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Industry best practices</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Program Delivery</h2>
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Powered by TeamBuildr</h3>
          <img src="/images/full-logo-white-orange.png" alt="TeamBuildr Logo" class="h-12 mb-6" />
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            All programming and communication is delivered through TeamBuildr, a professional training app that provides:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 mt-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Easy-to-follow workout instructions with video demonstrations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Progress tracking and performance metrics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Direct communication with your coach</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Who Is This For?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Aspiring strength and conditioning coaches</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Sport science students and graduates</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Performance professionals seeking growth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mt-1 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Anyone looking to advance their career in the fitness industry</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-8 border border-white/10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Start Your Mentorship Journey?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Take the first step towards advancing your career in the fitness industry with expert guidance.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-gray-200 transition duration-300">
              View Pricing
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-white/20 transition duration-300">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 